  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc0\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0baf\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Urea Fertilizer under Indian Loan Scheme - Govt",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The first phase of 65,000 metric tonnes of urea fertilizer pre-registered under the Indian loan scheme will reach the country on the 9th.",
        "In addition, Agriculture Minister Mahinda Amaraweera said that 110 million dollar relief loan will be available from the World Bank for the purchase of fertilizer for the big crop.",
        "He said this while announcing the weekly Cabinet decisions on Tuesday (5) during the press conference.",
        "The Power Minister has been advised to take steps to distribute fuel to the machines for harvesting the paddy crop and to the vehicles that transport the fertilizer.",
        "A ship will reach the country on Saturday 9th. This amount of fertilizer will be received from Oman through the Government of India.",
        "The first batch of 65,000 metric tonnes of pre-registered fertilizer, 40,000 metric tonnes, will reach the country on Saturday.",
        "The cargo ship, which left Oman port last Sunday, was scheduled to arrive in the country tonight (last night).",
        "However, it has been reported that its arrival has been delayed due to the cyclones that have occurred in the seas due to climate change. Once the ship arrives in the country, the fertilizer will be distributed to the farmers on a priority basis.",
        "In the first phase, 40,000 metric tons of fertilizer to reach the country has been decided to be provided for paddy cultivation and in the future 25,000 metric tons of fertilizer for grain cultivation and tea cultivation.",
        "Although urea is being sold at Rs 40,000 in the markets, we have decided to supply it at Rs 10,000. Farmers have expressed interest in this.",
        "The World Bank has agreed to provide a relief loan of $110 million for the mega project.",
        "Currently there is a call for tender for the same. Apart from this, the World Food Program has announced the distribution of 375,000 compost bags free of charge. It has been decided to provide it to low income earners.",
        "And M.O.P. and D.O.P. We have initiated negotiations with the Asian Development Bank and others regarding the assistance for the purchase of fertiliser. Our goal is to achieve successful results in the largest market. He said that all the programs for that are being continued."
      ],
